      <p class="card-text">Fishing is also an activity that creates feelings of self-fulfillment and success. Fishing requires skill and creates challenges to overcome. When you overcome challenges and learn the necessary skills to catch fish, you will feel a sense of accomplishment. Fishing is also an opportunity to bond with family or other friends.</p>
