      <details>
        <summary>Gardening</summary>
      <p class="card-text">Exposure to plants and the act of gardening can have a positive effect on mental health. You can enjoy the outdoors and all the beauty that plants have to offer by visiting one of Tampa is botanical gardens, or you can start a garden of your own and find joy in caring for it. You can find and grow plants that are native to Florida to benefit the environment. If you did rather take small steps toward gardening, you can start by taking care of house plants or succulents.</p>
